    "client_msg_id": "8da91b7e-e43e-4611-9e40-5feae4c5467e",
    "type": "message",
    "text": ":wave:  Hi folks. Surprised I didn’t find this community sooner, but glad this is a thing!\n\nI’m an art director, designer, and mediocre dev in London. Currently working at <http://egghead.io|egghead.io> (web dev educational platform) where I spend a lot of time designing and illustrating metaphors for programming concepts. Also helped co-create a book that uses visual diagrams to explain javascript: <http://justjavascript.com|justjavascript.com>. That project sent me down the rabbit hole of researching visual programming languages and alternate programming mediums. I was already a Victor/Kay/Engelbart/Xanadu obsessive, so it all comes full circle.\n\nI’m also a cultural anthropologist by training, and headed in an MSc in digital anthropology at UCL. Interested in the cultural dynamics of programming communities – specifically JavaScript-land since that’s where I tend to hang out. Glad to have found this corner of the web and always up for a chat with folks interested in the same topics.",
